5:
Look! There's something on the
ground here! I wonder if it's valuable.
9: What do you think, Sha Suzu?
13:
Upon closer inspection—yes!
This ore is perfect for armscraft!
I forbid you from selling it!
15:
Of course, it'll take no small amount of
professional knowledge to process it...
But that's where I come in!
19:
Uh, okay.
If you want it that much, here you go.
23: Are you going to forge a weapon?
27:
Heh-heh! You bet your ribbon!
It's going to be my greatest creation
to date!
30:
Our researchers at Voluntas
have been at it for years, but we still
don't know everything about
the weapons found in Kaleidoscope.
33:
Minus firearms, of course!
Such simple, elegant,
and intricate weapons...
34:
And perfectly reproducible!
After we deduced how to replicate
the firing mechanism, that is!
37:
Better yet, they give a bookworm
like me a fighting chance against
all the nastiest nasties!
40: Bask in the glory of engineering!
45:
Heh, wow. You sure are passionate,
aren't you, Sha Suzu?
49:
Oops, pardon me. Whenever I start
talking shop, I always get carried
away.
52:
Not just talking, though.
Back when we first met, you were
shooting that thing like crazy.
55:
The Kaleidoscope makes for a great
testing range!
What's better than moving targets!
58:
Heh,
that's what you call target practice?
60:
But, Sha Suzu, aren't you a student
at the Arcane Arts Academy?
Why don't you use, you know, magic?
63:
Well, anyone who studies at Voluntas
can use magic. That's a given.
65:
But now that I've gained a passion for
engineering firearms, I'm done with
all the hocus pocus!
67:
Who cares about grades or exams?
Especially while I have this little baby
to perfect!
72:
Whoa! You made that?
That's amazing!
76:
Oh, well, when you put it that way...
Yeah, I guess it is!
80: But you still require more ore, correct?
88:
Feast your peepers on that!
It's the exact material I need!
91:
Isn't this weird, though?
Like it was just asking to be found.
95:
Valor is the mother of invention,
as they say! Charge!
104:
No problem!
Thanks to my adjustments, my little
friend should be able to blow a hole in
this bucket just like that!
109:
It absorbed the bullets?
Wait, no! This cage is from Voluntas!
131:
Sha Suzu.
You are returning to the academy...
137:
Yes, this truant is at risk of repeating
a grade. And your distraction is
certainly no help.
